Element.removeAttributeNode doesn't consider the namespace of the attribute 
before trying to remove it. Therefore, removeAttributeNode will fail since it 
can't find the attribute in the list. Element.removeAttributeNode should be 
using NamedNodeMap.removeNamedItemNS(uri,name)

